  <brief_title>Effect Of The Consumption Of Fermented Dairy Drink On Common Infections In Shift-Workers</brief_title>
  <official_title>EFFECT OF THE CONSUMPTION OF FERMENTED DAIRY DRINK ON COMMON INFECTIONS IN SHIFT-WORKERS</official_title>
